{"type":null,"faqId":49891,"title":"华为智能手表_手表支持调节屏幕亮度吗？如何调节？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body51522882\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__p36366074174754\">如需改变屏幕亮度，您可以通过以下方式调节：</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__p60341448174754\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__b27618861174754\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__b14299331174754\">瞬时亮度调整：</strong></strong>三连击表冠，屏幕亮度会瞬间提亮并维持5秒。该操作主要在烈日、强光等不易观察到表盘的场景使用。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__p25034827174754\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__b11411181174754\">亮度调整：</strong>在手表主界面向左滑动一下，选择 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329187__b57323387174754\">设置 &gt; 调整亮度</strong>，滑动手指选择1-5来调节亮度。</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":636,"faqType":"屏幕显示类","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329187","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448616654000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"调节，屏幕，亮度","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}